      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. everything is just... dying. the oceans, the forests, the weather... it feels like we're just watching a slow motion car crash that we can't stop. i feel so stupid even trying to plan a future or go to school or anything, when the world is clearly just on its way out. like what is even the point of hanging on?",
